observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor instruct the:
 Inventory Committee to prepare the Report on the Physical Count of the Road Network System (RPCLRN) of the Municipality;
 Acting Municipal Treasurer to maintain a Local Road Inventory and Road Map and keep a complete Local Road Network Property Card for all roads and its components;
 Municipal Engineer to provide the Municipal Accountant and the Acting Municipal Treasurer with complete description and cost segregation of road components for road projects;
 Acting Municipal Treasurer to submit the list of government owned lot and lot with Deed of Donations to the Municipal Engineer; and
 Municipal Accountant to record the amount of road networks required in the transitory povision of COA Circular No. 2015-008
